FBIS4-13690 "drnes078_n_94008" FBIS-NES-94-078 Daily Report 22 Apr 1994 LEBANON Israeli Gunboats, Artillery Shell Southern Areas Israeli Gunboats, Artillery Shell Southern Areas NC2204102694 Beirut Radio Lebanon in Arabic 0900 GMT 22 Apr 94 NC2204102694 Beirut Radio Lebanon Arabic BFN [Text] Israeli gunboats opened fire at the al-'Izziyah area, near al-Qulaylah, after midnight last night. The enemy forces' artillery also shelled the area extending from al-Mansuri to Majdal Zun and the coastal stretch south of Tyre from their positions on al-Bayyad hill and al-Hardun at 0200 today. The shelling was accompanied by Israeli helicopter overflights.
